thread.title: Margaret Smith
thread.title_full: Paper Divas reviewed by Margaret Smith

author: Margaret Smith
title: Margaret Smith
text: I used one of the templates to create an invitation for my son's naming day. The day after I submitted the order a representative from PaperDivas rang to ask about what I was trying to achieve with some formatting and fixed it. The resulting product is high quality, professional and beautiful. I will definitely use this site again.
